    "desc": "A brand built on influencer innovation. We’re doing more than just monetizing the industry—we’re defining it.",
    "navbar": "COMPANY\nCREATOR\nBRAND\nNEWSROOM\nCAREERS\nENGLISH\nLOG IN",
    "text": "rewardStyle and LIKEtoKNOW.it are now LTK. Now, all partners will know us as one single global brand name: LTK.\nCOMPANY\nCREATOR\nBRAND\nNEWSROOM\nCAREERS\nENGLISH\nLOG IN\nA brand built on Creator innovation\n  We are driving more than $3B in annual brand sales by uniting Brands, Creators, and Shoppers through the power of distributed original content.\n  LTK Announces SoftBank Vision Fund 2 Investment\n\n\nLEARN MORE\n\n\nLEARN MORE\n\nDOWNLOAD LTK\n  LTK team\nSince 2011, LTK has grown from a few people in a studio apartment in Dallas, Texas to more than 350 team members worldwide.\n\n\nGeneral Counsel\nBrittany Degan\nCFO & GM, International\nJeff Dawson\nGM of Creator Platform\nNikki Kuritsky\nGM of Consumer Platform\nKit Ulrich\nGM of Brand Platform\nKristi O'Brien\nVP of People\nMeLinda Mccall\nChief Technology Officer\nTy Amell\n\nVIEW POSITIONS\nLISTEN NOW\nGET THE BOOK\nENGLISH\nFOLLOW US\nPodcast: Influencer Radio\n@shop.LTK\n@LTK.home\n@LTK.family\n@LTK.asia\n@LTK.europe\n@LTK.brasil\n@LTK.australia \nLEARN MORE\nLTK\nBecome a Creator\nBrand Platform\nNewsroom\nCompany\nCareers\nLEGAL\nTerms of Service\nPrivacy Policy\nCookie Policy\nDo Not Sell\nPatents\nSUPPORT\nGet Help\nContact Us\n© 2022 rewardStyle, Inc",
